    <briefdescription>
<para>Control block for a CMSIS-RTOSv2 memory pool. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Application can use manual user-defined allocation for RTOS objects by supplying a pointer to memory pool control block. Control block is initiazed within <computeroutput>osMemoryPoolNew()</computeroutput>. </para>
